The paper deals with the development of a new type of activation function for neural networks, which is a core topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the application of the proposed activation function in computer vision (cs.CV) and signal processing (cs.SI), which further supports these categories.
